CLIENT APPLICATIONS
-------------------

To compile programs against GEOS:

	CFLAGS += `geos-config --cflags`
	LDFLAGS += `geos-config --libs`

Headers inclusion (quick):

	// geometries, version and exceptions 
	#include <geos.h>

Headers inclusion (manual):

	// geometries
	#include <geos/geom.h>

	// exceptions
	#include <geos/util.h>

	// version
	#include <geos/version.h>

	... check documentation for more tips ...

Example usage:

	doc/example.cpp contains basic usage
	examples.

